			[5.584502, "o", "\n\u001b[1;24r\u001b[23;4H(1) If you use a non-POSIX locale (e.g., by setting ‘LC_ALL’ to\u001b[24;15H\u001b(B\u001b[0;1m\u001b[33m\u001b[44m3\u001b[22G2\u001b[H\u001b[39;49m\u001b(B\u001b[m"],
			[5.624317, "o", "\u001b[2;23r\u001b[23;1H"],
