			[6.465831, "o", "\u001b[11;3H\u001b(B\u001b[0;1m\u001b[31mSorting the output\n\u001b[3G\u001b[34mDetails about version sort\u001b[H\u001b[39m\u001b(B\u001b[m"],
			[6.617843, "o", "\u001b[10;3H\u001b(B\u001b[0;1m\u001b[31mWhat information is listed\n\u001b[3G\u001b[34mSorting the output\u001b[H\u001b[39m\u001b(B\u001b[m"],
			[6.969827, "o", "\u001b[10;3H\u001b(B\u001b[0;1m\u001b[34mWhat information is listed\n\u001b[3G\u001b[31mSorting the output\u001b[H\u001b[39m\u001b(B\u001b[m"],
			[7.442216, "o", "\u001b[1;30H\u001b(B\u001b[0;1m\u001b[33m\u001b[44mSorting the output,  Next: Details about version so\u001b[2;1Hrt,  Prev: What information is listed,  Up: ls invocation\u001b[39;49m\u001b(B\u001b[m"],
			[7.442914, "o", "\r\u001b[K\n10.1.3 Sorting the output\u001b[K\r\n-------------------------\r\n\u001b[K\n"],
			[7.443241, "o", "These options change the order in which ‘ls’ sorts the information it\r\noutputs.  By default, sorting is done by character code (e.g., ASCII\r\norder).\r\n\u001b[K\n‘-c’\u001b[K\r\n‘--time=ctime’\u001b[K\r\n‘--time=status’\u001b[K\n\u001b[5G\u001b[1K If the long listing format (e.g., ‘-l’, ‘-o’) is being used, print\n\u001b[5G\u001b[1K "],
			[7.44333, "o", "the status change timestamp (the ctime) instead of the mtime.  When\n\u001b[5G\u001b[1K explicitly sorting by time (‘--sort=time’ or ‘-t’) or when not\n\u001b[6G"],
			[7.443558, "o", "using a long listing format, sort according to the ctime.  *Note\r\n     \u001b(B\u001b[0;1m\u001b[31mFile timestamps\u001b(B\u001b[0m::.\u001b[K\r\n\n‘-f’\u001b[K\n\u001b[1K Primarily, like ‘-U’—do not sort; list the files in whatever order\n\u001b[5G\u001b[1K "],
			[7.444328, "o", "they are stored in the directory.  But also enable ‘-a’ (list all\n\u001b[5G\u001b[1K files) and disable ‘-l’, ‘--color’, and ‘-s’ (if they were\n\u001b[6Gspecified before the ‘-f’).\u001b[24;14H\u001b(B\u001b[0;1m\u001b[33m\u001b[44m23/68, 33%\u001b[K\u001b[H\u001b[39;49m\u001b(B\u001b[m"],
			[8.113889, "o", "\u001b[2;23r\u001b[23;1H"],
			[8.1142, "o", "\n\u001b[1;24r\u001b[24;15H\u001b(B\u001b[0;1m\u001b[33m\u001b[44m4\u001b[22G5\u001b[H\u001b[39;49m\u001b(B\u001b[m"],
			[8.774527, "o", "\u001b[2;23r\u001b[23;1H"],
			[8.774946, "o", "\n\u001b[1;24r\u001b[23;1H‘-r’\u001b[24;15H\u001b(B\u001b[0;1m\u001b[33m\u001b[44m5\u001b[22G6\u001b[H\u001b[39;49m\u001b(B\u001b[m"],
			[8.814466, "o", "\u001b[2;23r\u001b[23;1H"],
			[8.814805, "o", "\n\u001b[1;24r\u001b[23;1H‘--reverse’\n\u001b[15G\u001b(B\u001b[0;1m\u001b[33m\u001b[44m6\u001b[22G8\u001b[H\u001b[39;49m\u001b(B\u001b[m"],
			[8.854432, "o", "\u001b[2;23r\u001b[23;1H"],
			[8.854757, "o", "\n\u001b[1;24r\u001b[23;6HReverse whatever the sorting method is—e.g., list files in reverse\u001b[24;15H\u001b(B\u001b[0;1m\u001b[33m\u001b[44m7\u001b[22G9\u001b[H\u001b[39;49m\u001b(B\u001b[m"],
			[8.894176, "o", "\u001b[2;23r\u001b[23;1H"],
